  <h2>Getting Started with the Gumroad API</h2>
  <p>Did you know Gumroad has a powerful API that allows you to extend and integrate its functionality with your own applications and services? Whether you want to automate workflows, build custom dashboards, or create unique experiences for your customers, the Gumroad API provides the tools you need.</p>
  <h3>Key Capabilities:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Access product information.</li>
    <li>Retrieve sales data.</li>
    <li>Manage subscribers (for specific use cases, respecting privacy).</li>
    <li>Verify license keys.</li>
  </ul>
  <h3>Authentication:</h3>
  <p>Our API uses OAuth 2.0 for authentication, ensuring secure access to your data. You can create an application and generate API keys from your Gumroad settings.</p>
  <h3>Endpoints & Documentation:</h3>
  <p>Comprehensive documentation for all available endpoints, request parameters, and response formats can be found on our developer portal at <a href="/developers" target="_blank">gumroad.com/developers</a> (link placeholder, update with actual API docs link if different).</p>
